---
export const prerender = true;
---
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Attico Centro Storico — Casa &amp; Territorio</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
  <a href="/portfolio/immobiliare" class="back-btn">&larr; Torna agli Immobili</a>

  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <nav class="breadcrumb fade-in">
    <a href="/portfolio/immobiliare">Home</a>
    <span>/</span>
    <a href="/portfolio/immobiliare">Vendita</a>
    <span>/</span>
    <span class="current">Attico Centro Storico</span>
  </nav>

  <!-- Gallery -->
  <section class="gallery-section fade-in">
    <div class="gallery-grid">
      <div class="gallery-main" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e2e8f0,#cbd5e1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
        <span style="color:#94a3b8;font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:600;">Foto principale</span>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-thumbs">
        <div class="gallery-thumb" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#cbd5e1,#94a3b8);"></div>
        <div class="gallery-thumb" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#94a3b8,#64748b);"></div>
        <div class="gallery-thumb" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#64748b,#475569);"></div>
        <div class="gallery-thumb" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#475569,#334155);"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main content -->
  <section class="detail-section">
    <div class="detail-grid">
      <!-- Left: property info -->
      <div class="property-info fade-in">
        <div class="price-badge-row">
          <span class="property-price">&euro;385.000</span>
          <span class="badge badge-vendita">Vendita</span>
          <span class="badge badge-energy">Classe C</span>
        </div>
        <h1>Attico con terrazza panoramica</h1>
        <p class="property-location">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0118 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
          Verona, Centro Storico
        </p>

        <!-- Specs grid -->
        <div class="specs-grid">
          <div class="spec-item">
            <span class="spec-value">3</span>
            <span class="spec-label">Camere</span>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-item">
            <span class="spec-value">2</span>
            <span class="spec-label">Bagni</span>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-item">
            <span class="spec-value">145 m&sup2;</span>
            <span class="spec-label">Superficie</span>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-item">
            <span class="spec-value">4&deg;</span>
            <span class="spec-label">Piano</span>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-item">
            <span class="spec-value">S&igrave;</span>
            <span class="spec-label">Ascensore</span>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-item">
            <span class="spec-value">30 m&sup2;</span>
            <span class="spec-label">Terrazza</span>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-item">
            <span class="spec-value">1920</span>
            <span class="spec-label">Anno costruzione</span>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-item">
            <span class="spec-value">2022</span>
            <span class="spec-label">Ristrutturato</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Description -->
        <div class="description">
          <h2>Descrizione</h2>
          <p>Splendido attico nel cuore del centro storico di Verona, ultimo piano di un palazzo d'epoca completamente ristrutturato nel 2022. L'appartamento si sviluppa su 145 mq con doppia esposizione est-ovest che garantisce luminosit&agrave; tutto il giorno.</p>
          <p>Il soggiorno open space con travi a vista originali si apre sulla terrazza panoramica di 30 mq con vista sui tetti della citt&agrave;. Cucina abitabile con isola in marmo di Carrara, tre camere da letto di cui la principale con bagno en-suite e cabina armadio.</p>
          <p>Parquet in rovere originale restaurato, infissi in legno con doppio vetro, aria condizionata canalizzata. Posto auto in garage condominiale.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Caratteristiche -->
        <div class="features-section">
          <h2>Caratteristiche</h2>
          <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Terrazza panoramica
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Travi a vista
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Parquet originale
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Aria condizionata
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Ascensore
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Cantina
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Posto auto
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: agent + form -->
      <div class="sidebar fade-in">
        <!-- Agent card -->
        <div class="agent-card">
          <div class="agent-avatar">
            <div style="width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;background:#2563eb;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem;">LR</div>
          </div>
          <div class="agent-info">
            <h3>Laura Romani</h3>
            <p>Per informazioni e visite</p>
            <a href="tel:+39045800123" class="agent-phone">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 01-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 01-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 014.11 2h3a2 2 0 012 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 00.7 2.81 2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 002.81.7A2 2 0 0122 16.92z"/></svg>
              045 800 1234
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact form -->
        <div class="contact-form-wrap">
          <h3>Richiedi una Visita</h3>
          <form class="contact-form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault()">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label>Nome</label>
              <input type="text" placeholder="Mario Rossi" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label>Telefono</label>
              <input type="tel" placeholder="+39 333 123 4567" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label>Email</label>
              <input type="email" placeholder="mario@email.com" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label>Messaggio</label>
              <textarea rows="3" placeholder="Vorrei fissare una visita..."></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label>Preferenza orario</label>
              <select>
                <option>Mattina (9-12)</option>
                <option>Pomeriggio (14-17)</option>
                <option>Sera (17-19)</option>
                <option>Qualsiasi orario</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Invia Richiesta</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer style="text-align:center;padding:48px 24px 32px;color:#64748b;font-size:0.85rem;border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-weight:700;color:#1e293b;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:8px;">Casa &amp; Territorio Srl</p>
    <p>Via Verdi 12, 37121 Verona (VR) &mdash; Tel. 045 800 1234 &mdash; info@casaeterritorio.it</p>
    <p style="margin-top:8px;">P.IVA 04567890123 &mdash; &copy; 2026 Tutti i diritti riservati.</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.1 });
    document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  </script>

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; color: #1e293b; background: #f8fafc; overflow-x: hidden; }

    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #f1f5f9; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #2563eb; border-radius: 4px; }

    h1, h2, h3 { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; }
    p { margin-bottom: 1em; line-height: 1.7; }

    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
    }
    .fade-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    .gradient-text {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed);
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
    }

    .back-btn {
      position: fixed; top: 20px; left: 20px; z-index: 1000;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.2); color: #1e40af; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .back-btn:hover { background: rgba(37,99,235,0.1); transform: translateX(-4px); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(37,99,235,0.15); }

    /* Breadcrumb */
    .breadcrumb {
      max-width: 1200px; margin: 80px auto 0; padding: 16px 24px;
      font-size: 0.85rem; color: #64748b; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    }
    .breadcrumb a { color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
    .breadcrumb a:hover { opacity: 0.7; }
    .breadcrumb span { color: #94a3b8; }
    .breadcrumb .current { color: #1e293b; font-weight: 600; }

    /* Gallery */
    .gallery-section { max-width: 1200px; margin: 16px auto; padding: 0 24px; }
    .gallery-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
    .gallery-main { height: 400px; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; }
    .gallery-thumbs { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
    .gallery-thumb {
      border-radius: 12px; aspect-ratio: 1; transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .gallery-thumb:hover { transform: scale(1.03); }

    /* Detail section */
    .detail-section { max-width: 1200px; margin: 40px auto 60px; padding: 0 24px; }
    .detail-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px; gap: 40px; align-items: start; }

    /* Property info */
    .price-badge-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .property-price {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed);
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;
    }
    .badge-vendita { background: #2563eb; color: #fff; }
    .badge-energy { background: #fbbf24; color: #1e293b; }

    .property-info h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.3; }
    .property-location {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .specs-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .spec-item {
      background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; text-align: center;
      transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    }
    .spec-item:hover { border-color: rgba(37,99,235,0.3); box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(37,99,235,0.08); }
    .spec-value {
      display: block; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 800; color: #1e293b;
    }
    .spec-label { display: block; font-size: 0.75rem; color: #64748b; margin-top: 4px; }

    .description { margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .description h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .description p { color: #475569; font-size: 0.95rem; }

    .features-section h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }
    .feature-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #334155;
      padding: 8px 12px; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    /* Sidebar */
    .sidebar { position: sticky; top: 80px; }
    .agent-card {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
      background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .agent-info h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .agent-info p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .agent-phone {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; text-decoration: none;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .agent-phone:hover { opacity: 0.7; }

    .contact-form-wrap {
      background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px;
    }
    .contact-form-wrap h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .form-group label {
      display: block; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; color: #64748b;
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .form-group input, .form-group textarea, .form-group select {
      width: 100%; padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 10px;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #1e293b;
      background: #f8fafc; transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus, .form-group select:focus {
      outline: none; border-color: #2563eb; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(37,99,235,0.1);
    }
    .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; }
    .submit-btn {
      width: 100%; padding: 12px; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 12px;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .submit-btn:hover { background: #1d4ed8; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(37,99,235,0.3); }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .detail-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .sidebar { position: static; }
      .specs-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .gallery-main { height: 250px; }
      .gallery-thumbs { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
      .specs-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .breadcrumb { margin-top: 70px; }
      .back-btn { top: 12px; left: 12px; bottom: auto; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 8px 14px; }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>
